<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Gaon Rasoi — गाँव से, आपकी रसोई तक</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700;9..144,900&family=Mukta:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0a0906;
    --surface:#161310;
    --surface-alt:#1c1712;
    --text:#ffffff;
    --text-soft:#cfc6b0;
    --gold:#d4af37;
    --gold-deep:#a8841f;
    --gold-pale:#e9c869;
    --line: rgba(212,175,55,0.28);
    --line-soft: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--bg);
    color:var(--text);
    font-family:'Mukta', sans-serif;
    font-size:17px;
    line-height:1.6;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  h1,h2,h3, .display{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight:700;
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
    color:var(--text);
  }
  a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}
  img,svg{display:block; max-width:100%;}
  .wrap{max-width:1140px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 28px;}
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'Mukta', sans-serif;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:12.5px;
    letter-spacing:.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--gold);
  }

  /* ===== Header ===== */
  header{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    background:rgba(10,9,6,0.9);
    backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:16px 28px; max-width:1140px; margin:0 auto;
  }
  .logo{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-weight:700; font-size:22px;
    color:var(--text);
  }
  .logo-text{
    font-weight:900; font-size:24px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;
    background:linear-gradient(120deg, #fff3cf 0%, #e8c256 22%, #d4af37 45%, #f6dd8c 68%, #b8912a 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent;
    filter:drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(212,175,55,0.35));
  }
  .logo .devanagari{ color:var(--gold); font-size:15px; font-weight:600; font-family:'Mukta',sans-serif;}
  .logo-mark{width:34px; height:34px; flex-shrink:0;}
  nav.links{display:flex; gap:34px; font-weight:600; font-size:15px;}
  nav.links a{position:relative; padding:4px 0; color:var(--text-soft);}
  nav.links a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
  .nav-cta{
    background:var(--gold); color:#0a0906; padding:10px 20px;
    border-radius:3px; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; letter-spacing:.02em;
    border:1px solid var(--gold);
    transition:transform .15s ease, background .15s ease;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{ background:var(--text); border-color:var(--text); transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .menu-btn{display:none; flex-direction:column; gap:5px; background:none; border:0; cursor:pointer; padding:6px;}
  .menu-btn span{width:24px; height:2px; background:var(--gold); display:block;}

  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .hero{
    padding:76px 0 60px;
    position:relative;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.05fr 0.95fr; gap:50px; align-items:center;
  }
  .hero-text{ text-align:center; }
  .hero-text .lede{ margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; }
  .hero-ctas{ justify-content:center; }
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(46px, 6.2vw, 78px); line-height:0.98; margin:14px 0 8px; color:var(--text);}
  .gold-title{
    font-weight:900;
    background:linear-gradient(115deg, #fff6da 0%, #f0cd6a 18%, #d4af37 38%, #a8841f 52%, #e9c869 68%, #fff3cf 84%, #d4af37 100%);
    background-size:220% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent;
    filter:drop-shadow(0 0 22px rgba(212,175,55,0.45)) drop-shadow(0 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
    animation:shimmer 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    display:inline-block;
  }
  @keyframes shimmer{
    0%{background-position:0% 50%;}
    50%{background-position:100% 50%;}
    100%{background-position:0% 50%;}
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .gold-title{animation:none;}
  }
  .hero .hindi-line{
    font-family:'Mukta', sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:var(--gold);
    margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .hero p.lede{
    max-width:460px; color:var(--text-soft); font-size:17.5px; margin-bottom:30px;
  }
  .hero-ctas{display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--gold); color:#0a0906; padding:14px 26px; border-radius:3px;
    font-weight:700; font-size:15px; border:1px solid var(--gold);
    transition:transform .15s ease, background .15s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--gold-pale); border-color:var(--gold-pale); transform:translateY(-2px);}
  .btn-ghost{
    padding:14px 24px; border-radius:3px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;
    border:1.5px solid var(--gold); color:var(--text);
    transition:background .15s ease, transform .15s ease;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--gold); color:#0a0906; transform:translateY(-2px);}

  /* Hero illustration: shelf */
  .shelf{position:relative;}
  .seal{
    position:absolute; top:-18px; right:-6px; width:118px; height:118px;
    animation:spin 22s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes spin{ to{ transform:rotate(360deg);} }
  .shelf-board{
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:6px;
    padding:34px 28px 22px;
    box-shadow:0 24px 50px -20px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
  }
  .shelf-items{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:18px;}
  .shelf-item{
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    padding:12px 6px 14px;
    border-radius:4px;
    transition:transform .2s ease;
  }
  .shelf-item:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);}
  .shelf-item span{font-size:11.5px; font-weight:700; text-align:center; color:var(--text); letter-spacing:.01em;}
  .shelf-plank{
    height:10px; margin-top:6px;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold) 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 10px);
    opacity:.35; border-radius:2px;
  }

  /* ===== Story ribbon ===== */
  .story{
    background:var(--surface-alt); color:var(--text);
    padding:64px 0;
    position:relative;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .story-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:0.7fr 1.3fr; gap:40px; align-items:start;}
  .story h2{color:var(--text); font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,42px); margin-bottom:6px;}
  .story .eyebrow{color:var(--gold);}
  .story p{color:var(--text-soft); font-size:17px; max-width:620px;}
  .story p + p{margin-top:14px;}
  .story-quote{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-size:22px; font-style:italic; line-height:1.4;
    border-left:3px solid var(--gold); padding-left:20px; color:var(--text);
  }

  /* ===== Products ===== */
  .section{padding:88px 0;}
  .section-head{max-width:600px; margin-bottom:48px;}
  .section-head h2{font-size:clamp(32px,4.4vw,46px); margin-top:10px; color:var(--text);}
  .section-head p{color:var(--text-soft); margin-top:14px; font-size:17px;}

  .products-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr); gap:22px;
  }
  .card{
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--line-soft);
    border-radius:6px;
    padding:26px 22px 24px;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px;
    transition:transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, border-color .2s ease;
    opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px);
  }
  .card.revealed{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
  .card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow:0 20px 40px -18px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
    border-color:var(--gold);
  }
  .card .icon-wrap{
    width:56px; height:56px; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--surface-alt);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .card .icon-wrap svg{width:32px; height:32px;}
  .card h3{font-size:19px; margin-top:2px; color:var(--text);}
  .card p{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--text-soft); line-height:1.55;}
  .card .tag{
    margin-top:auto; font-size:11.5px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold);
  }
  .card.span-2{grid-column:span 2;}
  .card.span-4{grid-column:span 4;}
  .variant-list{
    margin-top:auto; padding-top:10px; border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:9px;
  }
  .variant-row{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; gap:14px;
  }
  .variant-name{font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text);}
  .variant-sizes{
    font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--gold); white-space:nowrap;
    letter-spacing:.01em;
  }
  .tea-card{gap:22px;}
  .chip-list{
    margin-top:auto; padding-top:12px; border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft);
    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;
  }
  .chip{
    font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text);
    border:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--surface-alt);
    border-radius:20px; padding:5px 12px;
  }
  .tea-card-head{display:flex; gap:18px; align-items:flex-start;}
  .tea-card-head .icon-wrap{flex-shrink:0;}
  .tea-card-head h3{font-size:20px; margin-bottom:6px;}
  .tea-card-head p{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--text-soft); max-width:520px;}
  .tea-groups{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr; gap:30px;
    padding-top:16px; border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }
  .tea-group h4{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:var(--gold);
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .tea-note{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--text-soft);}
  .tea-sub{margin-bottom:16px;}
  .tea-sub:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  .tea-sub-label{
    display:block; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.06em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--text); margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .tea-list{list-style:none; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:5px;}
  .tea-list li{
    font-size:14px; color:var(--text-soft); padding-left:16px; position:relative;
  }
  .tea-list li::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; left:0; top:9px; width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--gold);
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px){
    .card.span-2{grid-column:span 2;}
    .card.span-4{grid-column:span 2;}
    .tea-groups{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px){
    .card.span-2{grid-column:span 1;}
    .card.span-4{grid-column:span 1;}
    .variant-row{flex-direction:column; gap:2px;}
    .tea-card-head{flex-direction:column;}
  }

  /* ===== Lab report banner ===== */
  .lab-banner{
    background:var(--surface);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:26px 0;
  }
  .lab-banner-inner{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .lab-icon{
    width:48px; height:48px; flex-shrink:0; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--surface-alt); border:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .lab-icon svg{width:26px; height:26px;}
  .lab-text{
    flex:1; min-width:240px; font-size:16.5px; color:var(--text);
  }
  .lab-text strong{color:var(--gold);}
  .lab-cta{
    flex-shrink:0; border:1.5px solid var(--gold); color:var(--text);
    padding:10px 20px; border-radius:3px; font-weight:700; font-size:14px;
    transition:background .15s ease, color .15s ease, transform .15s ease;
  }
  .lab-cta:hover{background:var(--gold); color:#0a0906; transform:translateY(-2px);}

  /* ===== Quality pillars ===== */
  .pillars{background:var(--surface-alt); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .pillars-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:30px;
  }
  .pillar{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;}
  .pillar .num{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:var(--gold);
  }
  .pillar h3{font-size:19px; color:var(--text);}
  .pillar p{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--text-soft);}
  .pillar-divider{width:36px; height:3px; background:var(--gold); border-radius:2px;}

  /* ===== CTA / Contact ===== */
  .contact{
    background:#050403; color:var(--text);
  }
  .contact .wrap{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr; gap:50px; align-items:center;
  }
  .contact h2{color:var(--text); font-size:clamp(30px,4.2vw,44px);}
  .contact p{color:var(--text-soft); margin-top:14px; max-width:440px;}
  .contact-box{
    background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px;
    padding:30px;
  }
  .contact-row{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }
  .contact-row:last-child{border-bottom:0;}
  .contact-row .label{font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-soft);}
  .contact-row .value{font-weight:600; font-size:15.5px; color:var(--text);}
  .contact-cta{
    display:block; margin-top:22px; text-align:center;
    background:var(--gold); color:#0a0906; font-weight:700;
    padding:14px; border-radius:4px; transition:background .15s ease, transform .15s ease;
  }
  .contact-cta:hover{background:var(--gold-pale); transform:translateY(-2px);}

  footer{
    background:#050403; color:var(--text-soft); padding:26px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft);
    font-size:13.5px;
  }
  footer .wrap{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;}

  @media (max-width: 880px){
    nav.links, .nav-cta{display:none;}
    .menu-btn{display:flex;}
    .hero-grid, .story-grid, .contact .wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .products-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .pillars-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); row-gap:34px;}
    .shelf{margin-top:10px;}
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px){
    .products-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .pillars-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .hero{padding-top:40px;}
    .shelf-items{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    html{scroll-behavior:auto;}
    .seal{animation:none;}
    .card{transition:none; opacity:1; transform:none;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="nav">
    <div class="logo">
      <svg class="logo-mark" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
        <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="19" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <path d="M20 9 C15 15 13 20 13 24 C13 29 16 32 20 32 C24 32 27 29 27 24 C27 20 25 15 20 9Z" fill="#d4af37"/>
        <path d="M20 14 C17 18 16 21 16 24 C16 27 18 29 20 29" stroke="#0a0906" stroke-width="1.1" fill="none"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="logo-text">Gaon Rasoi</span> <span class="devanagari">गाँव रसोई</span>
    </div>
    <nav class="links">
      <a href="#products">Products</a>
      <a href="#story">Our Story</a>
      <a href="#quality">Why Us</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Get in touch</a>
    <button class="menu-btn" aria-label="Menu" id="menuBtn"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="eyebrow">Kirana staples, done the honest way</p>
      <h1><span class="gold-title">Gaon Rasoi</span></h1>
      <p class="hindi-line">गाँव से, आपकी रसोई तक</p>
      <p class="lede">Cold-pressed mustard oil, stone-ground atta, and pickles made the way a village kitchen makes them — sourced close to the ground, packed close to home.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#products" class="btn-primary">See our products</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-ghost">Talk to us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="shelf">
      <svg class="seal" viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none">
        <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="52" fill="#161310" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="43" fill="none" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2 3"/>
        <path id="sealCircle" d="M60,17 a43,43 0 1,1 -0.1,0" fill="none"/>
        <text font-family="Mukta, sans-serif" font-size="8.4" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="2" fill="#ffffff">
          <textPath href="#sealCircle" startOffset="2%">GAON RASOI • SHUDH • TAAZA •</textPath>
        </text>
        <path d="M60 44 C55 50 52 55 52 60 C52 66 55 70 60 70 C65 70 68 66 68 60 C68 55 65 50 60 44Z" fill="#d4af37"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="shelf-board">
        <div class="shelf-items">
          <div class="shelf-item">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><path d="M15 6h10v6l4 4v18a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H13a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V16l4-4V6Z" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M13 20h14" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M15 24h10v8H15z" fill="#d4af37"/></svg>
            <span>Mustard Oil</span>
          </div>
          <div class="shelf-item">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><circle cx="14" cy="24" r="5" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="24" cy="18" r="6" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="28" cy="27" r="4.5" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
            <span>Dry Fruits</span>
          </div>
          <div class="shelf-item">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><path d="M10 18h16v8a8 8 0 0 1-8 8 8 8 0 0 1-8-8v-8Z" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M26 20h3a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-3" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M14 12c1 2-1 3 0 5M20 12c1 2-1 3 0 5" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.4"/></svg>
            <span>Everyday Tea</span>
          </div>
          <div class="shelf-item">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><path d="M10 18h16v8a8 8 0 0 1-8 8 8 8 0 0 1-8-8v-8Z" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M26 20h3a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-3" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M18 10l2 4 2-4" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.4" fill="#d4af37"/></svg>
            <span>Flavoured Tea</span>
          </div>
          <div class="shelf-item">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><path d="M11 15h18l-2 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H15a2 2 0 0 1-2-2L11 15Z" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M14 15c0-4 2-7 6-7s6 3 6 7" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M15 20h10M15 25h10" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.2"/></svg>
            <span>Multigrain Atta</span>
          </div>
          <div class="shelf-item">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><rect x="12" y="14" width="16" height="18" rx="2" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M20 14V9M16 12l4-4 4 4" stroke="#d4af37" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="20" cy="23" r="4" fill="#d4af37"/></svg>
            <span>Pickles</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="shelf-plank"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="wrap story-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Why "Gaon Rasoi"</p>
      <h2>The village kitchen,<br>brought to your shelf.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>Every jar of achaar and every litre of kachi ghani oil we sell starts the same way — in a small mill or a village kitchen, made in the unhurried way it's always been made.</p>
      <p>We work directly with growers, chakkis and home producers to keep that process intact, so what reaches your kitchen still tastes like it came from one.</p>
      <div style="height:26px"></div>
      <p class="story-quote">"Asli swaad, gaon wala — the real taste, the village way."</p>
    </div>
